web.archive.org/web/20120722042743/http://treintaytres.gub.uy/web/ Official Website]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20121010053238/http://www.ine.gub.uy/mapas/censos2011/para%20colgar%20en%20web/pdf/19_UYTT/Localidades/A0H_19220_19723_19956%20Treinta%20y%20Tres%20y%20otras.pdf INE map of Treinta y Tres, Ejido de Treinta y Tres & Villa Sara]\n\n{{Treinta y Tres Department}}\n[[Category:Populated places in the Treinta y Tres Department]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1853]]\n", "text_old": "{{other uses|33 (disambiguation)}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| official_name           = Treinta y Tres\n| other_name              = \n| settlement_type         = Capital city\n| image_skyline           = Parque del R\u00edo Olimar.jpg\n| image_caption           = Bridges over the River Olimar\n| image_map               = \n| image_shield            = Coat_of_arms_of_Treinta_y_Tres_Department.png\n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = Uruguay\n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Uruguay\n| coordinates             = {{coord|33|14|0|S|54|23|0|W|region:UY-TT|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|Uruguay}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[Departments of Uruguay|Department]]\n| subdivision_name1       = {{flag|Treinta y Tres}}\n| established_title       = \n| established_date        = \n| leader_title            = \n| leader_name             = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| area_land_km2           = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_total        = 25477\n| population_as_of        = 2011 Census\n| population_density_km2  = \n| population_blank1_title = [[Demonym]]\n| population_blank1       = olimare\u00f1o,-a\n| timezone                = [[UTC]] -3\n| postal_code_type        = Postal code\n| postal_code             = 33000\n| area_code_type          = [[Telephone numbers in Uruguay|Dial plan]]\n| area_code               = +598 445 (+5 digits)\n| blank_name              = [[K\u00f6ppe